===Noun===
'''chutzpah'''
#[[Audacity]], [[effrontery]] or [[impudence]]
#: ''I wish I had more '''chutzpah''' when I was at school - I was a very boring child.''

==== Usage note ====
When used by Jews, chutzpah is considered a very bad thing to have. Non-Jews tend to use it in a much more positive way.

